    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a concours-level E46 M3, a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333hp through six individual throttle bodies and a high-precision dual-VANOS system. The drivetrain is anchored by a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual and a factory limited-slip differential. Mechanically flawless, the subframe has been proactively reinforced, and the rod bearings and VANOS hub have been addressed to ensure peak operational integrity. The chassis remains rigid, supported by a meticulously maintained suspension and staggered Style 67 wheels wrapped in fresh Michelin Pilot Sport 4S rubber. A true collector-grade specimen with zero deferred maintenance and pristine original paint.",
      "price": 48500.0,
