      "description": "Presented in showroom condition, this vehicle is a true collector-grade specimen. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish with zero rock chips or swirl marks, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in an untouched state; the premium leather seats show no signs of wear, and the original factory scent persists. Mechanically, it is flawless, having been strictly garage-kept and maintained exclusively by certified technicians with a full, documented service history. Every button, sensor, and mechanical component functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that has been meticulously preserved by a single owner with no expense spared.",
